1
00:00:18,237 --> 00:00:19,829
Xiao Xiao, stay in here

2
00:00:19,872 --> 00:00:22,238
no matter what, don't come out, okay?

3
00:00:24,143 --> 00:00:26,373
I'll be right behind the wall

4
00:00:36,322 --> 00:00:39,018
In 370BC, the Warring States China

5
00:00:39,058 --> 00:00:41,117
Zhao Nation dispatched 100,000 warriors

6
00:00:41,160 --> 00:00:44,061
led by Xiang Yanzhong,
to attack Yan Nation

7
00:00:44,097 --> 00:00:46,327
LIANG stands right on his path to Yan

8
00:00:46,366 --> 00:00:49,233
There's no way she can
resist Zhao's mighty troop

9
00:00:49,268 --> 00:00:51,634
and will be definitely taken as buffer

10
00:00:52,472 --> 00:00:54,804
Their only chance for survival is to

11
00:00:54,841 --> 00:00:56,240
ask for the help of Mozi warrior

12
00:00:56,275 --> 00:00:59,005
who are experts in defending

13
00:00:59,679 --> 00:01:00,976
but...

14
00:01:01,013 --> 00:01:05,143
as Liang teeters on the edge of peril

15
00:01:05,184 --> 00:01:07,049
Mozi warriors...

16
00:01:07,086 --> 00:01:08,986
still didn't arrive

17
00:01:19,465 --> 00:01:22,798
Father, we must fight

18
00:01:24,103 --> 00:01:28,403
Zhao's Commander
Xiang Yanzhong is a brilliant strategist

19
00:01:28,441 --> 00:01:32,810
His advance troop has already arrived

20
00:01:32,845 --> 00:01:35,109
We have to take action now

21
00:01:35,648 --> 00:01:38,481
before the arrival of their main force

22
00:01:38,518 --> 00:01:40,918
we must surrender

23
00:01:40,953 --> 00:01:44,946
otherwise, we're all done for

24
00:01:48,694 --> 00:01:51,788
Fighting with bare hands...

25
00:01:52,498 --> 00:01:54,090
ends up the same...

26
00:01:54,834 --> 00:01:56,028
My Lord

27
00:01:58,438 --> 00:01:59,769
My Lord

28
00:01:59,806 --> 00:02:04,106
what if the Mozi army
were to make it here?

29
00:02:08,214 --> 00:02:10,546
Assemble at the Gate, quick

30
00:02:10,583 --> 00:02:12,517
Get the horses ready

31
00:02:12,552 --> 00:02:13,985
Move on, quick

32
00:02:17,223 --> 00:02:18,554
Hurry up

33
00:02:23,863 --> 00:02:25,228
Come on, hurry up

34
00:02:29,535 --> 00:02:30,934
Cavalry Chief

35
00:02:30,970 --> 00:02:32,733
Who told you to ride out?

36
00:02:32,772 --> 00:02:34,000
Your Majesty's decree

37
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:36,099
All cavaliers await at the South Gate

38
00:02:36,142 --> 00:02:37,734
for General Niu's order

39
00:02:38,444 --> 00:02:41,971
General, the surrender notes
and cavaliers are ready

40
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:13,175
Open the Gate

41
00:03:13,212 --> 00:03:15,578
Open the Gate

42
00:03:46,445 --> 00:03:49,414
Someone's approaching from the West

43
00:04:06,899 --> 00:04:08,764
Who are you?

44
00:04:13,706 --> 00:04:15,469
Mozi, Ge Li

45
00:04:15,508 --> 00:04:19,035
Mozi has finally arrived

46
00:04:25,117 --> 00:04:26,015
Open the Gate

47
00:04:26,052 --> 00:04:28,418
Open the Gate

48
00:04:38,364 --> 00:04:39,558
Take this

49
00:04:40,466 --> 00:04:42,024
Zhao soldiers... they're here

50
00:04:56,983 --> 00:04:58,780
Zhao's hostile force

51
00:05:00,186 --> 00:05:02,416
They're furious, shall we inform the King?

52
00:05:10,096 --> 00:05:11,290
Who are you?

53
00:05:11,330 --> 00:05:14,424
How dare you trespasses on our camp site

54
00:05:14,467 --> 00:05:17,732
This is General Niu of LIANG

55
00:05:19,005 --> 00:05:22,441
I'm here to deliver the surrender note

56
00:05:28,381 --> 00:05:33,250
Send cavaliers to pass them
our surrender decision

57
00:05:33,285 --> 00:05:34,252
Yes

58
00:05:46,332 --> 00:05:47,856
Attack

59
00:05:54,607 --> 00:05:58,441
You think surrendering and not fighting

60
00:05:58,477 --> 00:06:00,308
can please the Zhao?

61
00:06:00,346 --> 00:06:02,405
And stop the war?

62
00:06:02,448 --> 00:06:03,813
Zhao's army is huge

63
00:06:03,849 --> 00:06:06,477
you want us all to get killed?

64
00:06:20,900 --> 00:06:24,631
When they take over Liang,
you'll still have to suffer

65
00:06:25,404 --> 00:06:26,564
Ministers will be killed

66
00:06:31,444 --> 00:06:32,911
soldiers will be captured

67
00:06:34,747 --> 00:06:37,272
your families will be ruined

68
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:43,152
women will be dishonored

69
00:06:43,189 --> 00:06:44,816
Why?

70
00:06:44,857 --> 00:06:47,587
Are you contented with this?

71
00:06:49,495 --> 00:06:52,089
Why don't you give a try?

72
00:06:52,932 --> 00:06:54,229
Though...

73
00:06:55,101 --> 00:06:56,534
we may die in the battle

74
00:06:57,903 --> 00:06:59,962
but at least you'd tried

75
00:07:00,005 --> 00:07:01,632
and if we can make it

76
00:07:01,674 --> 00:07:04,404
we'll make it worth

77
00:07:04,443 --> 00:07:05,774
We can't give up our homeland

78
00:07:05,811 --> 00:07:07,108
What shall we do then?

79
00:07:07,146 --> 00:07:08,238
Sir, please lead us to defend

80
00:07:08,280 --> 00:07:11,875
Yes, lead us

81
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,815
Take action now, Mozi

82
00:07:15,855 --> 00:07:18,756
Zhao army is already here

83
00:08:01,834 --> 00:08:04,564
Can you give me your bow?

84
00:08:04,603 --> 00:08:06,264
Their distance is too far

85
00:08:06,305 --> 00:08:07,704
Give me

86
00:08:22,855 --> 00:08:25,881
To fight or surrender?

87
00:08:27,726 --> 00:08:31,594
No one is allowed to intrude into my city

88
00:08:55,621 --> 00:08:56,952
Protect the General

89
00:09:06,465 --> 00:09:08,092
General Gao...

90
00:09:11,036 --> 00:09:12,833
General Wei commanded us to retreat?

91
00:09:14,006 --> 00:09:17,169
Retreat

92
00:09:17,209 --> 00:09:18,437
Thank you

93
00:09:18,477 --> 00:09:21,469
Good job, they'd retreated

94
00:09:21,513 --> 00:09:23,674
They are only the vanguard troop

95
00:09:23,716 --> 00:09:25,479
It's just the beginning

96
00:09:28,354 --> 00:09:30,652
Retreat

97
00:09:36,562 --> 00:09:38,029
Your majesty

98
00:09:38,063 --> 00:09:39,087
Proceed

99
00:09:40,065 --> 00:09:44,161
A Mozi arrived and
drove away the Zhao's vanguard

100
00:09:44,203 --> 00:09:45,363
Congratulations, My Lord

101
00:09:45,404 --> 00:09:48,771
Liang is saved

102
00:09:59,285 --> 00:10:00,946
Nonsense

103
00:10:05,891 --> 00:10:07,654
My Lord, please take care

104
00:10:11,130 --> 00:10:12,290
My Lord...

105
00:10:13,198 --> 00:10:14,529
My Lord...

106
00:10:18,203 --> 00:10:20,694
Your Honor, the King was drunk

107
00:10:26,278 --> 00:10:28,075
Back off, the Prince is coming

108
00:10:28,113 --> 00:10:30,081
Come on, good boy

109
00:10:40,793 --> 00:10:42,693
The King is not feeling well

110
00:10:43,395 --> 00:10:45,590
your request had to be put back later

111
00:10:46,432 --> 00:10:49,265
Enemies are right outside,
we don't have much time

112
00:10:49,301 --> 00:10:50,893
By the way

113
00:10:51,470 --> 00:10:53,097
which cities have you protected before?

114
00:10:56,976 --> 00:10:58,341
This is my first time

115
00:10:59,178 --> 00:11:00,736
You are the only one they sent?

116
00:11:02,181 --> 00:11:05,548
How about the jade pendant?

117
00:11:06,785 --> 00:11:08,616
Did you bring it?

118
00:11:08,654 --> 00:11:10,349
It's still in the Mozi Hall

119
00:11:12,224 --> 00:11:14,886
It was our token for Mozi's help

120
00:11:14,927 --> 00:11:16,895
How can you forget?

121
00:11:17,730 --> 00:11:19,061
Let me have a look

122
00:11:19,098 --> 00:11:19,996
General Wei

123
00:11:20,032 --> 00:11:21,624
why...

124
00:11:22,968 --> 00:11:24,765
Just a little modification...

125
00:11:25,771 --> 00:11:28,797
and double the shooting range

126
00:11:30,909 --> 00:11:33,002
Why do you stop my attack?

127
00:11:33,045 --> 00:11:34,945
What for?

128
00:11:34,980 --> 00:11:37,210
We don't need to attack

129
00:11:37,816 --> 00:11:40,717
Liang had already sent
someone here to surrender

130
00:11:42,988 --> 00:11:45,718
Then, why are they shooting me?

131
00:11:48,327 --> 00:11:49,419
Give out my order

132
00:11:50,229 --> 00:11:53,164
block off all the paths to Liang

133
00:11:53,198 --> 00:11:56,759
poison all its water source.

134
00:11:56,802 --> 00:12:00,203
No one is to go near Liang
without my order

135
00:12:00,239 --> 00:12:01,729
Yes

136
00:12:01,774 --> 00:12:03,935
That just...

137
00:12:03,976 --> 00:12:06,069
gives them time to defend

138
00:12:10,149 --> 00:12:12,208
Don't worry

139
00:12:12,251 --> 00:12:15,118
we'll discuss
when the Commander arrives

140
00:12:16,455 --> 00:12:18,650
Sir, Prince Liang Shi offered...

141
00:12:20,626 --> 00:12:24,392
you to rest here for the night

142
00:12:25,998 --> 00:12:27,522
Thank you

143
00:12:49,321 --> 00:12:51,482
Thank you

144
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,502
Cavalry Chief

145
00:13:18,016 --> 00:13:21,008
Who did the arrangement?
He's here to protect us

146
00:13:21,053 --> 00:13:21,985
It's the Prince's order...

147
00:13:22,020 --> 00:13:23,487
The Prince? How can he...

148
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:38,135
My Prince was convinced by an outsider

149
00:13:38,170 --> 00:13:42,163
and stimulated the Zhao's vanguard

150
00:13:42,207 --> 00:13:44,835
They will definitely retaliate.

151
00:13:44,877 --> 00:13:46,845
I'm sure your majesty understands

152
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:51,213
What is your suggestion?

153
00:13:53,418 --> 00:13:55,283
Your servant believes that...

154
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:58,847
Don't hesitate? Say it.

155
00:14:00,759 --> 00:14:04,855
Ge Li persuaded the people

156
00:14:04,897 --> 00:14:09,061
and offended the Zhao
against your decree

157
00:14:09,101 --> 00:14:11,501
We must arrest Ge Li

158
00:14:11,537 --> 00:14:13,698
and hand him over to the Zhao

159
00:14:13,739 --> 00:14:17,038
That will placate them

160
00:14:17,075 --> 00:14:20,567
and show My Lord's sincerity

161
00:14:20,612 --> 00:14:24,446
If Xiang Yanzhong and his troops arrive

162
00:14:24,483 --> 00:14:27,509
Liang will be in great danger

163
00:14:29,688 --> 00:14:32,714
Royal Tutor wants me to...

164
00:14:32,758 --> 00:14:35,090
turn against the Mozi?

165
00:14:35,627 --> 00:14:36,924
My Lord

166
00:14:37,529 --> 00:14:41,465
this is the only way to save Liang

167
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:46,267
What about the Mozi?

168
00:14:46,305 --> 00:14:48,398
They would be furious

169
00:14:49,107 --> 00:14:54,170
Ge Li didn't bring the pendant you sent

170
00:14:55,180 --> 00:14:57,512
his identity is unclear

171
00:14:59,551 --> 00:15:01,348
My Lord

172
00:15:01,386 --> 00:15:02,751
Proceed

173
00:15:02,788 --> 00:15:05,586
The Prince came to see
your majesty with Mozi Ge Li

174
00:15:08,727 --> 00:15:12,595
Bring Ge Li to the Main Hall alone

175
00:15:12,631 --> 00:15:13,859
Yes

176
00:15:21,773 --> 00:15:27,006
Long live My Lord

177
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:42,686
Ge Li

178
00:15:42,728 --> 00:15:43,752
Yes

179
00:15:43,795 --> 00:15:47,629
I've heard that you've never lead troops

180
00:15:47,666 --> 00:15:50,726
or protect a city before

181
00:15:51,370 --> 00:15:55,033
Facing Xiang Yanzhong's force

182
00:15:55,073 --> 00:16:00,067
how will you save Liang?

183
00:16:00,112 --> 00:16:03,275
Zhao's target is Yan Nation

184
00:16:03,315 --> 00:16:07,581
they won't risk their mission on Liang

185
00:16:07,619 --> 00:16:11,680
The battle with Liang
must be fast and clear

186
00:16:12,758 --> 00:16:14,157
Survival or not

187
00:16:14,192 --> 00:16:17,252
depends on how long Liang can hold

188
00:16:17,296 --> 00:16:20,197
How long will it take to repel the Zhao?

189
00:16:20,232 --> 00:16:26,296
If Liang can hold up to one month,
Zhao will retreat

190
00:16:29,041 --> 00:16:31,009
Ge Li

191
00:16:31,877 --> 00:16:34,402
You think...

192
00:16:34,446 --> 00:16:36,380
how long can Liang hold?

193
00:16:36,415 --> 00:16:40,317
That's up to your trust on me

194
00:16:40,352 --> 00:16:42,843
I trust you unquestionably

195
00:16:42,888 --> 00:16:44,150
Then, I urged you to

196
00:16:44,189 --> 00:16:47,022
hand over all command to Ge Li

197
00:16:48,894 --> 00:16:52,352
The utmost care must be taken

198
00:16:52,397 --> 00:16:54,592
orders must be clear & strict

199
00:16:54,633 --> 00:16:56,863
efficiency is most important

200
00:16:59,971 --> 00:17:01,302
Right

201
00:17:03,475 --> 00:17:07,138
Right

202
00:17:09,348 --> 00:17:11,976
It seems that...

203
00:17:12,017 --> 00:17:16,249
Liang is going for a long siege

204
00:17:16,955 --> 00:17:18,320
Yes

205
00:17:18,357 --> 00:17:21,520
But what if...

206
00:17:21,560 --> 00:17:26,793
...I mean if you were killed?

207
00:17:26,832 --> 00:17:29,494
What else can we do?

208
00:17:30,168 --> 00:17:31,658
How about...

209
00:17:31,703 --> 00:17:35,400
not fighting?

210
00:17:40,645 --> 00:17:42,112
Not to fight?

211
00:17:42,147 --> 00:17:43,671
Right

212
00:17:46,418 --> 00:17:49,683
That's all on your will

213
00:17:50,288 --> 00:17:51,983
My will is strong for that

214
00:17:58,463 --> 00:18:01,227
Then tie up Ge Li now

215
00:18:02,801 --> 00:18:04,769
let Prince Liang Shi...

216
00:18:06,071 --> 00:18:08,005
bring him to the Zhao

217
00:18:09,207 --> 00:18:12,370
That will stop the war

218
00:18:13,578 --> 00:18:17,344
You can bring along your families

219
00:18:17,382 --> 00:18:19,942
go to Zhao Nation

220
00:18:19,985 --> 00:18:22,647
and plead for forgiveness

221
00:18:23,522 --> 00:18:28,425
You then hand over Liang to the Zhao

222
00:18:29,761 --> 00:18:35,199
All men will become slaves

223
00:18:35,233 --> 00:18:36,165
Then...

224
00:18:36,201 --> 00:18:40,604
the people of Liang will suffer no war

225
00:18:41,440 --> 00:18:45,399
If your majesty prefers this

226
00:18:45,444 --> 00:18:49,278
Fine, Ge Li will do all he can

227
00:18:49,314 --> 00:18:50,781
Please

228
00:19:39,564 --> 00:19:41,395
The king sees his people as everything

229
00:19:42,601 --> 00:19:45,934
My decision is... at all costs

230
00:19:46,705 --> 00:19:48,673
Liang Shi

231
00:19:50,542 --> 00:19:51,873
Yes

232
00:19:53,078 --> 00:19:57,674
You must obey Ge Li's command

233
00:19:57,716 --> 00:19:59,843
Apart from the Royal guards

234
00:19:59,885 --> 00:20:03,753
Mozi Ge Li will command all troops

235
00:20:03,788 --> 00:20:06,689
to resist Zhao's invasion

236
00:20:06,725 --> 00:20:11,389
Anyone who disobeys his orders will be...

237
00:20:11,429 --> 00:20:13,021
be-headed

238
00:20:15,634 --> 00:20:20,594
Our enemy will poison our water source

239
00:20:21,106 --> 00:20:22,664
from now on

240
00:20:22,707 --> 00:20:26,609
we must not use any water
flowing into Liang

241
00:20:26,645 --> 00:20:30,979
We'll have to dig more wells in the city

242
00:20:31,016 --> 00:20:35,180
Collect farmer's harvest

243
00:20:35,220 --> 00:20:37,188
select several locations in the city

244
00:20:37,222 --> 00:20:38,883
as food storages

245
00:20:38,924 --> 00:20:41,757
All food and water
will be under distribution

246
00:20:41,793 --> 00:20:43,852
Direct all water drainage

247
00:20:43,895 --> 00:20:46,830
to the farmland and let it swamp

248
00:20:46,865 --> 00:20:48,992
Swamp the farmland?

249
00:20:49,034 --> 00:20:51,298
We'll starve ourselves of food

250
00:20:51,336 --> 00:20:53,861
With appropriate allocation

251
00:20:53,905 --> 00:20:56,965
our coffers will last us for a year

252
00:20:57,008 --> 00:20:58,942
Then what?

253
00:20:58,977 --> 00:21:00,945
We'll have kept the city

254
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:03,871
but there'll be nothing left

255
00:21:03,915 --> 00:21:08,284
If we lose our lives,
what good will come of that?

256
00:21:08,320 --> 00:21:09,685
Even if we block off the East

257
00:21:09,721 --> 00:21:12,417
enemies will attack us
from other directions

258
00:21:14,159 --> 00:21:16,957
The west and north
give us natural barriers

259
00:21:16,995 --> 00:21:19,429
Enemies will not
attack from those directions

260
00:21:19,464 --> 00:21:21,625
How about the south?

261
00:21:21,666 --> 00:21:23,156
Why don't we spend more effort on it?

262
00:21:23,201 --> 00:21:26,602
Every city must have one weakness

263
00:21:26,638 --> 00:21:31,075
this is where our enemies will attack

264
00:21:31,109 --> 00:21:33,475
so as to control their attack

265
00:21:34,412 --> 00:21:36,846
Gather all the strong men

266
00:21:36,881 --> 00:21:41,944
we've to build a bulwark
at the south in seven days

267
00:21:42,687 --> 00:21:45,952
Can that be done?

268
00:21:45,991 --> 00:21:46,980
Mr. Ge Li

269
00:21:47,025 --> 00:21:49,391
how can we build a bulwark
in such a short time?

270
00:21:49,427 --> 00:21:50,951
It would take at least a year

271
00:21:50,996 --> 00:21:53,692
to bring the stones from the mountain

272
00:21:53,732 --> 00:21:56,701
Knocking down the palace wall?

273
00:21:57,736 --> 00:21:59,966
How can you protect the palace?

274
00:22:00,005 --> 00:22:01,529
Are you revolting?

275
00:22:05,443 --> 00:22:10,210
These stones are for building a bulwark

276
00:22:10,915 --> 00:22:12,610
The bulwark

277
00:22:13,752 --> 00:22:16,619
is our first line of defense

278
00:22:17,489 --> 00:22:19,457
If we lose the city

279
00:22:19,491 --> 00:22:22,119
the palace will be lost too

280
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:25,994
Protecting the city means
protecting the palace

281
00:22:26,031 --> 00:22:28,363
Ge Li

282
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:31,927
can a bulwark built in such a short tim

283
00:22:31,970 --> 00:22:35,371
defend Xiang Yanzhong's troop?

284
00:22:35,407 --> 00:22:38,672
To defend Liang in such a way...

285
00:22:38,710 --> 00:22:40,837
This is not only defending

286
00:22:40,879 --> 00:22:45,680
it's also a psychological tactic

287
00:22:47,652 --> 00:22:52,180
