00:52:46,483 --> 00:52:48,644
It isn't worth much

584
00:52:48,685 --> 00:52:50,346
please keep it

585
00:52:51,654 --> 00:52:56,648
Mozi shouldn't accept gifts

586
00:52:56,693 --> 00:52:58,320
or else

587
00:52:58,361 --> 00:53:02,593
people will think we are
helping others for their return

588
00:53:02,632 --> 00:53:04,259
Not accepting gifts

589
00:53:04,300 --> 00:53:06,860
doesn't mean no one suspect you

590
00:53:19,182 --> 00:53:20,774
Wait...

591
00:53:22,819 --> 00:53:24,411
You'd better stay in here

592
00:53:24,454 --> 00:53:25,944
there're lots of people outside

593
00:53:27,123 --> 00:53:29,785
Mr. Ge Li has recovered

594
00:53:41,204 --> 00:53:45,436
Commander, we can't
postpone attacking Yan

595
00:53:45,475 --> 00:53:47,204
My suggestion is...

596
00:53:47,243 --> 00:53:50,076
Let's leave 4,000 soldiers guarding Liang

597
00:53:50,113 --> 00:53:53,776
they'll surrender when they
run out of food and water

598
00:53:53,816 --> 00:53:55,044
then...

599
00:53:55,084 --> 00:53:58,247
we can then
take revenge for General Gao

600
00:53:58,288 --> 00:54:00,756
Commander, what do you think?

601
00:54:02,392 --> 00:54:05,384
This battle is no longer a personal affair

602
00:54:05,428 --> 00:54:08,158
Liang seems meaningless to us, but...

603
00:54:08,197 --> 00:54:10,665
we under-estimated our enemies,
and were defeated

604
00:54:11,901 --> 00:54:13,630
You think...

605
00:54:13,670 --> 00:54:17,231
we can defeat Yan
with our dispirited troops?

606
00:54:17,273 --> 00:54:19,366
Do we have this courage?

607
00:54:21,711 --> 00:54:25,875
I would like to have
opinions from other Generals

608
00:55:05,088 --> 00:55:08,023
This dagger has poison

609
00:55:08,057 --> 00:55:10,252
someone dropped it into my house

610
00:55:10,293 --> 00:55:12,454
They're already here...

611
00:55:12,495 --> 00:55:14,588
even if we don't do it...

612
00:55:15,264 --> 00:55:18,529
they'll do it

613
00:55:28,578 --> 00:55:32,241
You don't want to kill Ge Li, right?

614
00:55:33,583 --> 00:55:35,847
You must have forgotten
your wife and son...

615
00:55:36,919 --> 00:55:38,284
No

616
00:55:38,321 --> 00:55:40,949
he came here to protect us

617
00:55:40,990 --> 00:55:42,855
How can we do that?

618
00:55:45,028 --> 00:55:46,290
Protect us?

619
00:55:46,329 --> 00:55:48,058
He is giving up our lives

620
00:55:48,097 --> 00:55:50,065
by putting us in the front line?

621
00:55:50,099 --> 00:55:53,557
We're just lucky to be still alive

622
00:55:54,637 --> 00:55:57,401
Even if we'd killed Ge Li...

623
00:55:57,440 --> 00:56:00,204
can we save our families?

624
00:56:00,243 --> 00:56:02,768
If we kill Ge Li...

625
00:56:02,812 --> 00:56:05,280
who's going to save Liang?

626
00:56:10,186 --> 00:56:11,380
I know where he is...

627
00:56:23,099 --> 00:56:25,260
Take it

628
00:56:25,301 --> 00:56:26,427
Go

629
00:56:26,469 --> 00:56:27,595
Go

630
00:56:32,975 --> 00:56:34,442
Everybody listen

631
00:56:34,477 --> 00:56:35,910
no matter what, armor or swords

632
00:56:35,945 --> 00:56:38,812
collect all the useful stuffs

633
00:56:40,950 --> 00:56:41,917
What are you doing?

634
00:56:49,559 --> 00:56:51,720
Why do you want to kill me?

635
00:56:51,761 --> 00:56:52,386
Drop the knife

636
00:56:52,428 --> 00:56:54,157
Stay away

637
00:56:54,197 --> 00:56:56,688
Guards

638
00:56:59,235 --> 00:57:00,634
Drop the weapon

639
00:57:09,946 --> 00:57:12,073
Mr. Ge Li, he's dead

640
00:57:22,992 --> 00:57:25,893
I've one important announcement today

641
00:57:25,928 --> 00:57:27,793
But before I announce

642
00:57:27,830 --> 00:57:29,855
let's give a...

643
00:57:29,899 --> 00:57:32,527
silent meditation to Pu Le,
who died yesterday

644
00:57:34,737 --> 00:57:36,796
As usual

645
00:57:37,774 --> 00:57:39,173
close your eyes

646
00:57:39,208 --> 00:57:41,267
until the 10th stroke

647
00:57:54,056 --> 00:57:55,318
Traitor

648
00:58:03,666 --> 00:58:05,156
Little girl...

649
00:58:05,201 --> 00:58:06,463
don't be afraid

650
00:58:08,704 --> 00:58:11,195
why do you have to come to Liang?

651
00:58:12,842 --> 00:58:15,936
It must be the Zhao
assigned her to kill Mr. Ge Li

652
00:58:15,978 --> 00:58:18,037
Right, why do you want to kill Mr. Ge Li

653
00:58:18,080 --> 00:58:19,445
Quiet

654
00:58:22,218 --> 00:58:23,947
Bastard, how dare you are

655
00:58:23,986 --> 00:58:28,116
Don't let her go! Kill her

656
00:58:28,157 --> 00:58:29,249
Stop

657
00:58:29,859 --> 00:58:30,826
Back off

658
00:58:31,427 --> 00:58:32,621
Back off

659
00:59:28,751 --> 00:59:30,184
Mr. Ge Li

660
00:59:31,387 --> 00:59:32,877
Where are you going?

661
00:59:36,058 --> 00:59:37,685
I'd like to make myself clear

662
00:59:39,095 --> 00:59:42,553
Mozi will not accept any gifts

663
00:59:43,833 --> 00:59:45,858
Thanks for your gesture

664
01:00:28,005 --> 01:00:29,472
Sir

665
01:00:29,506 --> 01:00:31,269
Why do you follow me?

666
01:00:31,308 --> 01:00:33,538
You nearly got killed! Go back

667
01:00:35,112 --> 01:00:37,410
Aren't you going to spy on Zhao Camp?

668
01:00:37,447 --> 01:00:39,142
I always came here riding with the horses

669
01:00:39,182 --> 01:00:40,911
I'm familiar with this area

670
01:00:41,451 --> 01:00:42,816
Follow me

671
01:00:44,621 --> 01:00:46,179
You're not going

672
01:00:46,990 --> 01:00:48,582
This way is the shortcut

673
01:00:56,333 --> 01:00:58,563
What are they carrying?

674
01:00:58,602 --> 01:01:00,092
Soil

675
01:01:00,137 --> 01:01:02,264
They're digging a tunnel...

676
01:01:05,042 --> 01:01:06,532
To Liang?

677
01:01:15,485 --> 01:01:17,282
Why are they dumping it into the stream?

678
01:01:17,320 --> 01:01:20,756
The stream will wash away the soil

679
01:01:22,459 --> 01:01:24,586
then, no one will know

680
01:01:24,628 --> 01:01:28,394
how far they had dug

681
01:01:28,432 --> 01:01:30,059
Let's go

682
01:01:31,068 --> 01:01:32,433
Someone is up there

683
01:01:44,681 --> 01:01:46,376
There they are

684
01:01:46,416 --> 01:01:47,781
Get them

685
01:02:03,100 --> 01:02:04,567
Can you swim?

686
01:02:08,839 --> 01:02:10,602
Go, don't worry about me

687
01:02:10,640 --> 01:02:11,800
Go, quick

688
01:02:16,980 --> 01:02:17,969
Stop running

689
01:02:18,014 --> 01:02:20,209
Surrender or you'll die here

690
01:02:20,250 --> 01:02:21,182
You'll have to save me

691
01:02:23,186 --> 01:02:24,517
Move

692
01:03:12,335 --> 01:03:13,302
Breathe

693
01:03:15,105 --> 01:03:16,800
You're...

694
01:03:16,840 --> 01:03:18,467
very brave

695
01:03:19,676 --> 01:03:22,338
If I didn't jump...

696
01:03:23,480 --> 01:03:25,038
would you jump?

697
01:03:25,081 --> 01:03:26,605
I would

698
01:03:26,650 --> 01:03:28,675
But I'll kill you first

699
01:03:30,353 --> 01:03:32,947
Is that what you Mozi
would have done sanely?

700
01:03:33,657 --> 01:03:36,148
You think killing you is rational?

701
01:03:36,193 --> 01:03:37,888
How are you going to kill me?

702
01:03:42,532 --> 01:03:44,261
Push you down the waterfall

703
01:03:47,804 --> 01:03:49,533
Do you feel better now?

704
01:03:49,573 --> 01:03:51,370
Can you walk by yourself?

705
01:04:02,652 --> 01:04:04,449
Quiet

706
01:04:10,660 --> 01:04:12,389
There's nothing
in the West City and the barn

707
01:04:12,429 --> 01:04:14,363
where are they going to attack?

708
01:04:15,131 --> 01:04:18,259
They'll dig a few tunnels,
there'll be more than one exit

709
01:04:18,301 --> 01:04:21,566
we can't be sure whether
we had blocked them all

710
01:04:23,306 --> 01:04:25,433
I'm not blocking them off

711
01:04:25,475 --> 01:04:26,874
I'm letting them in

712
01:04:26,910 --> 01:04:28,070
No

713
01:04:28,111 --> 01:04:31,205
they must be collaborating
with the force outside

714
01:04:32,182 --> 01:04:34,013
I know

715
01:04:34,050 --> 01:04:37,178
we're going to defeat
our enemies in a dragnet

716
01:04:37,821 --> 01:04:39,049
After ten days

717
01:04:39,089 --> 01:04:43,719
we can dig three tunnels
in here, here and here

718
01:04:43,760 --> 01:04:44,920
Commander, what do you think?

719
01:04:44,961 --> 01:04:47,054
Can you speed up the process?

720
01:04:47,097 --> 01:04:50,555
If our soldiers can enter the City

721
01:04:50,600 --> 01:04:52,864
Liang will not be able to defend

722
01:04:54,771 --> 01:04:56,932
Three days later

723
01:04:56,973 --> 01:04:59,134
will be the advent of winter

724
01:04:59,175 --> 01:05:02,167
Longer night time
is an advantage for our attack

725
01:05:02,212 --> 01:05:03,179
Commander

726
01:05:03,213 --> 01:05:07,741
Someone was spying on us
a few days ago...

727
01:05:07,784 --> 01:05:10,275
The longer we take

728
01:05:10,320 --> 01:05:14,154
our enemies may
find out the tunnel exits

729
01:05:14,190 --> 01:05:16,283
Gather all the slaves

730
01:05:18,795 --> 01:05:20,160
three days later

731
01:05:20,196 --> 01:05:22,960
we'll attack from here

732
01:06:24,894 --> 01:06:26,589
Warriors, get ready

733
01:06:45,014 --> 01:06:46,879
Commander...

734
01:07:05,402 --> 01:07:07,427
The exit was blocked, move back

735
01:07:09,873 --> 01:07:13,070
Attack

736
01:07:14,677 --> 01:07:16,338
Pull

737
01:07:40,270 --> 01:07:42,101
Drop your weapons

738
01:07:42,138 --> 01:07:43,867
and your lives will be spared

739
01:08:02,692 --> 01:08:04,853
They're here

740
01:08:08,198 --> 01:08:10,257
I'm just a slave

741
01:08:10,300 --> 01:08:11,767
I don't want to come

742
01:08:11,801 --> 01:08:12,495
Stop him

743
01:08:12,535 --> 01:08:13,900
let me go

744
01:08:14,771 --> 01:08:15,931
Kill him

745
01:08:15,972 --> 01:08:17,371
What are you doing? Please let her down

746
01:08:18,575 --> 01:08:20,839
Stay back

747
01:08:20,877 --> 01:08:24,574
Please... please, let her go...

748
01:08:26,883 --> 01:08:29,977
Please... please, let her go...

749
01:08:30,787 --> 01:08:32,755
Please... don't...

750
01:08:32,789 --> 01:08:34,586
he'll really kill my sister

751
01:08:34,624 --> 01:08:36,353
The Zhao force me

752
01:08:36,392 --> 01:08:37,552
I don't want to come

753
01:08:37,594 --> 01:08:38,583
Please, please...

754
01:08:38,628 --> 01:08:40,027
Please give her back to me

755
01:08:40,063 --> 01:08:44,090
Please let her down

756
01:08:44,133 --> 01:08:44,997
Stay back

757
01:08:45,034 --> 01:08:46,899
No please

758
01:08:48,404 --> 01:08:49,962
Let her go...

759
01:08:50,006 --> 01:08:52,201
let the child go

760
01:08:52,242 --> 01:08:53,209
She's innocent

761
01:08:53,243 --> 01:08:55,711
I just know how to dig tunnels

762
01:08:55,745 --> 01:08:57,679
they force me to come

763
01:08:59,148 --> 01:09:00,672
Get ready

764
01:09:01,284 --> 01:09:02,615
Kill

765
01:09:04,020 --> 01:09:05,248
Shoot

766
01:09:13,897 --> 01:09:15,831
Defeating enemies in a dragnet

767
01:09:26,709 --> 01:09:27,971
Quiet

768
01:09:28,011 --> 01:09:29,478
Xiao Xiao, it's okay

769
01:09:30,914 --> 01:09:32,176
Let go of the child

770
01:09:32,949 --> 01:09:34,974
I promise

771
01:09:35,018 --> 01:09:37,213
no one will hurt you

772
01:09:40,323 --> 01:09:41,790
Give her to me

773
01:09:41,824 --> 01:09:43,849
Please...

774
01:09:43,893 --> 01:09:45,622
Give me

775
01:09:54,037 --> 01:09:54,833
Xiao-xiao...

776
01:09:54,871 --> 01:09:57,032
Xiao-xiao...

777
01:10:00,310 --> 01:10:01,402
Stop

778
01:10:02,178 --> 01:10:02,837
Let him go

779
01:10:03,446 --> 01:10:04,435
Stop

780
01:10:06,282 --> 01:10:07,078
Stop

781
01:10:08,251 --> 01:10:09,218
Stop

782
01:10:10,486 --> 01:10:11,612
Stop

783
01:10:14,390 --> 01:10:15,550
Move back

784
01:10:16,259 --> 01:10:17,317
Move back

785
01:10:17,360 --> 01:10:18,327
Everybody back

786
01:10:18,361 --> 01:10:19,623
Everybody move back

787
01:10:19,662 --> 01:10:20,458
Sir, are you alright?

788
01:10:20,496 --> 01:10:21,554
I'm fine

789
01:10:21,598 --> 01:10:23,122
All of you assemble at the Square

790
01:10:23,166 --> 01:10:25,100
Hurry Up! Go

791
01:10:25,134 --> 01:10:27,500
Are you okay? Did you get hurt?

792
01:11:05,842 --> 01:11:07,469
Let's go back

793
01:11:13,683 --> 01:11:15,207
Don't come back

794
01:11:16,185 --> 01:11:20,053
Go along the stream, you'll not be found

795
01:11:25,228 --> 01:11:27,560
Why don't you kill me?

796
01:11:33,302 --> 01:11:36,032
Why do you ask such a foolish question?

797
01:11:39,208 --> 01:11:41,267
Why...

798
01:11:41,310 --> 01:11:43,403
should people kill each other?

799
01:11:55,358 --> 01:11:58,156
I must take revenge for you

800
01:11:59,796 --> 01:12:02,560
It's all my fault

801
01:12:02,598 --> 01:12:06,500
I shouldn't make you suffer

802
01:12:06,536 --> 01:12:09,130
They're inhuman

803
01:12:33,896 --> 01:12:35,488
Congratulations on
your astounding victory

804
01:12:35,531 --> 01:12:37,158
The King would like to reward you

805
01:12:38,701 --> 01:12:40,396
Please come with me to the Palace

806
01:12:43,740 --> 01:12:45,332
Reward?

807
01:12:47,610 --> 01:12:49,840
General Niu...

808
01:12:49,879 --> 01:12:53,337
can't you see all these dead bodies?

809
01:12:53,916 --> 01:12:55,349
They were our enemies

810
01:12:55,384 --> 01:12:57,409
Aren't they humans?

811
01:12:58,521 --> 01:13:03,151
When enemies is trying to kill me

812
01:13:03,192 --> 01:13:06,753
I'll have to defend or even kill him

813
01:13:07,530 --> 01:13:10,431
but killing someone because of hatred...

814
01:13:10,466 --> 01:13:12,400
it's absolutely wrong

815
01:13:13,436 --> 01:13:15,199
What a pity

816
01:13:15,705 --> 01:13:19,505
Every man has his weak point

817
01:13:20,543 --> 01:13:24,206
Mozi Philosophy is not
for ruling a country

818
01:13:24,947 --> 01:13:30,408
This Mozi clan will fall...

819
01:13:35,458 --> 01:13:37,255
I'd like to be excused

820
01:13:38,027 --> 01:13:41,827
You seem very appreciative of Ge Li

821
01:13:44,200 --> 01:13:46,498
I acknowledge his defending skills

822
01:13:46,536 --> 01:13:50,097
That's where it should end

823
01:13:50,139 --> 01:13:56,374
Mozi philosophy is only
applicable in times of war

824
01:13:56,412 --> 01:14:01,440
They're not suitable in times of peace

825
01:14:01,484 --> 01:14:04,282
You must be clear on this

826
01:14:04,320 --> 01:14:07,756
Yes, my Lord is right

827
01:14:07,790 --> 01:14:09,280
Understood

828
01:14:18,234 --> 01:14:20,065
Watch him closely

829
01:14:20,102 --> 01:14:20,659
Yes

830
01:14:20,703 --> 01:14:22,933
don't let him getting off the track

831
01:14:22,972 --> 01:14:24,462
Yes

832
01:14:24,507 --> 01:14:26,304
General Niu

833
01:14:26,342 --> 01:14:27,104
Yes

834
01:14:27,143 --> 01:14:29,168
you must pay close attention

835
01:14:29,212 --> 01:14:33,205
all those revolting thoughts

836
01:14:33,249 --> 01:14:35,740
shall never spread in Liang

837
01:14:35,785 --> 01:14:36,752
Yes

838
01:14:53,102 --> 01:14:54,729
Are you okay?

839
01:14:58,474 --> 01:14:59,941
I'm fine

840
01:15:03,112 --> 01:15:04,841
The weather is getting cold...

841
01:15:04,881 --> 01:15:06,371
I know you don't have
any warm clothing...

842
01:15:06,415 --> 01:15:09,976
so I took out my father's coat
and see if it fits or not

843
01:15:10,019 --> 01:15:12,544
I can adjust it...

844
01:15:13,489 --> 01:15:16,151
Just fit, thanks

845
01:15:18,160 --> 01:15:20,685
I'll return it when I leave

846
01:15:22,098 --> 01:15:24,089
When?

847
01:15:24,867 --> 01:15:27,301
I'll leave when this battle is over

848
01:15:29,405 --> 01:15:31,305
The battle should be over soon...

849
01:15:31,908 --> 01:15:33,170
very soon

850
01:15:43,920 --> 01:15:46,616
Did you go to the Square last night?

851
01:15:47,723 --> 01:15:49,281
No

852
01:15:49,325 --> 01:15:52,783
You assigned me
to keep guard in the North

853
01:15:52,828 --> 01:15:55,092
I'd heard the Zhao army was defeated

854
01:15:55,131 --> 01:15:57,190
Many of them died...

855
01:16:00,202 --> 01:16:02,500
lots of them

856
01:16:04,974 --> 01:16:07,135
They're still...

857
01:16:07,877 --> 01:16:10,869
moving their bodies out for burial

858
01:16:12,548 --> 01:16:16,484
Defeating enemies
in a dragnet... is that right?

859
01:16:37,173 --> 01:16:38,470
I remembered

860
01:16:38,507 --> 01:16:41,965
my father told me this
when I was a little girl...

861
01:16:43,079 --> 01:16:48,881
When you start questioning
what is right or wrong

862
01:16:48,918 --> 01:16:51,944
you are uncertain with
your faith and beliefs

863
01:17:05,267 --> 01:17:08,202
Is it only war can make you stay?

864
01:17:14,043 --> 01:17:15,408
I thought...

865
01:17:15,444 --> 01:17:17,969
you are always looking for peace

866
01:17:31,594 --> 01:17:33,118
Sorry...

867
01:17:35,664 --> 01:17:37,689
What for?

868
01:17:52,081 --> 01:17:54,311
You're always like that...

869
01:17:56,419 --> 01:17:59,855
You're so protective with everything you do

870
01:18:00,956 --> 01:18:03,823
You always ask whether you're right or not

871
01:18:06,462 --> 01:18:09,090
Is it really that important?

872
01:18:09,999 --> 01:18:11,899
Even if you know it's right

873
01:18:11,934 --> 01:18:15,028
but for some people...

874
01:18:15,071 --> 01:18:17,369
they prefers to be wrong

875
01:18:20,209 --> 01:18:22,370
I would want to tell you

876
01:18:23,579 --> 01:18:25,843
no matter it's right or wrong

877
01:18:27,249 --> 01:18:29,740
I just want to be with you

878
01:18:36,392 --> 01:18:40,226
You talk about universal love all the time

879
01:18:43,199 --> 01:18:45,133
You should know how to love

880
01:18:46,068 --> 01:18:47,592
you know

881
01:18:56,979 --> 01:18:58,276
Ge Li arrives...

882
01:18:58,314 --> 01:18:59,906
Liang will survive

883
01:18:59,949 --> 01:19:01,678
Ge Li stays...

884
01:19:01,717 --> 01:19:03,617
Liang will be safe

885
01:19:03,652 --> 01:19:04,949
Ge Li goes...

886
01:19:04,987 --> 01:19:07,080
Liang cannot hold

887
01:19:07,123 --> 01:19:09,057
How about if Ge Li leaves?

888
01:19:18,134 --> 01:19:20,034
Just those small pieces?

889
01:19:21,203 --> 01:19:23,398
Anyway, melt it quickly

890
01:19:31,814 --> 01:19:33,873
Commander

891
01:19:42,625 --> 01:19:44,456
It is time to retreat

892
01:19:49,798 --> 01:19:52,961
News from our spy who
returned from Zhao Nation

893
01:19:53,002 --> 01:19:54,469
Proceed

894
01:19:55,004 --> 01:19:56,699
News from Zhao Nation

895
01:19:56,739 --> 01:19:58,400
The King of Qi has ordered
an army of 200,000

896
01:19:58,440 --> 01:20:00,408
setting off five days ago
to attack Zhao Nation

897
01:20:00,442 --> 01:20:02,672
Zhao Nation is preparing for the war

898
01:20:03,846 --> 01:20:05,609
Thanks for your majesty's blessing

899
01:20:05,648 --> 01:20:07,013
If that is the case

900
01:20:07,049 --> 01:20:09,882
Xiang Yanzhong will be called back

901
01:20:09,919 --> 01:20:11,978
Liang will be saved

902
01:20:12,021 --> 01:20:14,285
Liang will be saved

903
01:20:15,457 --> 01:20:20,360
However, the news of
Zhao's retreat must not spread

904
01:20:20,396 --> 01:20:21,761
I plead My Lord

905
01:20:21,797 --> 01:20:26,200
to withdraw all power from
Ge Li immediately

906
01:20:26,235 --> 01:20:27,725
otherwise, people will think it is Ge Li

907
01:20:27,770 --> 01:20:31,103
who defeated the Zhao troops

908
01:20:31,140 --> 01:20:33,734
We have to demolish any chance

909
01:20:33,776 --> 01:20:39,408
for Ge Li's supporters to rebel

910
01:20:40,249 --> 01:20:44,618
You think Ge Li will rebel, General?

911
01:20:45,788 --> 01:20:47,619
I don't think so

912
01:20:47,656 --> 01:20:49,419
Why are you so sure?

913
01:20:49,458 --> 01:20:50,117
Because...

914
01:20:50,159 --> 01:20:52,389
Because there is no such need

915
01:20:53,295 --> 01:20:57,095
Ge Li's popularity

916
01:20:57,132 --> 01:20:59,100
is now higher than the King

917
01:20:59,969 --> 01:21:02,233
he doesn't need to do a thing

918
01:21:03,172 --> 01:21:04,434
Right?

919
01:21:09,445 --> 01:21:14,883
Someone defending Liang
under false pretenses

920
01:21:15,618 --> 01:21:22,046
and initiates rebellion by
imposing personal adoration

921
01:21:22,091 --> 01:21:24,719
Doesn't it sound the same as rebel?

922
01:21:24,760 --> 01:21:27,160
General, what do you think?

923
01:21:28,964 --> 01:21:33,458
I agree with Royal Tutor
but lack of evidence

924
01:21:34,270 --> 01:21:35,202
General Niu

925
01:21:35,237 --> 01:21:36,033
Yes

926
01:21:36,071 --> 01:21:37,538
if you restores your military power

927
01:21:38,207 --> 01:21:42,701
would you be able to put down the riot?

928
01:21:43,846 --> 01:21:46,940
And arrest all the rebels?

929
01:22:38,801 --> 01:22:40,359
They're back

930
01:22:41,503 --> 01:22:42,902
How's it?

931
01:22:54,717 --> 01:22:55,877
Commander

932
01:22:58,887 --> 01:23:02,186
Liang must think that we had retreated

933
01:23:02,224 --> 01:23:06,456
We're just left with 1,000 soldiers

934
01:23:07,062 --> 01:23:08,757
Commander

935
01:23:09,431 --> 01:23:12,457
shall we call back part of
our army for the attack?

936
01:23:13,435 --> 01:23:15,562
Victory will come

937
01:23:16,338 --> 01:23:18,670
when there's no way to retreat

938
01:23:19,341 --> 01:23:22,242
This battle has to be fast and clear

939
01:23:22,277 --> 01:23:24,837
We'll end this up with Ge Li

940
01:24:00,616 --> 01:24:02,277
New boots?

941
01:24:14,696 --> 01:24:16,220
No problem, Mr. Ge Li

942
01:24:16,265 --> 01:24:18,495
it will be ready when you come back

943
01:24:20,335 --> 01:24:23,862
I disagreed on the massacre last night, but...

944
01:24:23,906 --> 01:24:26,067
You can't stop them...

945
01:24:28,177 --> 01:24:30,475
I always think that killing enemies
is a kind of glory...

946
01:24:33,115 --> 01:24:35,242
where will you go after the battle ends?

947
01:24:37,953 --> 01:24:40,945
Wherever needs me, I'll be there

948
01:24:45,894 --> 01:24:50,024
What if Zhao is being
invaded and ask for your help

949
01:24:50,065 --> 01:24:51,726
will you go?

950
01:24:51,767 --> 01:24:53,394
Of course I would

951
01:24:54,970 --> 01:24:57,029
You've wiped out their army

952
01:24:57,739 --> 01:25:00,173
then turn around and save their lives?

953
01:25:00,209 --> 01:25:02,336
Those you'd defeated before...

954
01:25:02,377 --> 01:25:04,777
will they accept your help?

955
01:25:08,617 --> 01:25:10,551
Frankly speaking

956
01:25:11,820 --> 01:25:13,447
I'm never sure

957
01:25:14,590 --> 01:25:16,683
whether those people I had helped

958
01:25:17,926 --> 01:25:21,089
really appreciate what I've done for them...

959
01:25:22,631 --> 01:25:27,193
Then, Mozi's universal love
is just blind talking?

960
01:25:30,506 --> 01:25:32,633
Nothing is perfect

961
01:25:33,442 --> 01:25:35,307
I just want no regrets in my life

962
01:25:36,678 --> 01:25:38,145
Blacksmith

963
01:25:38,180 --> 01:25:41,843
is the pot ready?

964
01:25:41,884 --> 01:25:42,908
Sure

965
01:25:42,951 --> 01:25:45,351
Mr. Ge Li is a true hero

966
01:25:45,387 --> 01:25:47,082
He's humble and skilled

967
01:25:47,122 --> 01:25:50,819
Just the opposite to our royals

968
01:25:51,093 --> 01:25:54,460
If our King got a bit of his talent

969
01:25:54,496 --> 01:25:57,021
Liang will be undefeatable

970
01:26:00,235 --> 01:26:01,429
Mr. Ge Li

971
01:26:02,137 --> 01:26:03,365
Mr. Ge Li

972
01:26:03,405 --> 01:26:04,633
we are all set

973
01:26:04,673 --> 01:26:05,799
Let's go

974
01:26:05,841 --> 01:26:07,934
Is this really going to work?

975
01:26:07,976 --> 01:26:09,876
That's psychological tactic

976
01:26:09,912 --> 01:26:13,313
Can you really cook Zhao food?

977
01:26:13,348 --> 01:26:16,715
I can guarantee that
the Zhaos will be miss home-

978
01:26:16,752 --> 01:26:18,049
Here are the firewoods

979
01:26:18,086 --> 01:26:19,053
Put it here

980
01:26:20,255 --> 01:26:20,949
Thank you

981
01:26:20,989 --> 01:26:22,650
Pass me the seasoning

982
01:26:22,691 --> 01:26:23,885
Mr. Ge Li...

983
01:26:26,762 --> 01:26:27,694
How is it?

984
01:26:27,729 --> 01:26:29,856
There's no one is the Zhao camp

985
01:26:29,898 --> 01:26:30,523
They retreated?

986
01:26:30,566 --> 01:26:32,796
Yes. It's abandoned. Nothing's there

987
01:26:32,834 --> 01:26:35,496
You guys first go back.
I'll go and check it out

988
01:26:38,941 --> 01:26:40,340
Come on

989
01:26:40,375 --> 01:26:41,740
Let's have some meat

990
01:26:43,979 --> 01:26:46,106
Is that Zhao's food? What a great smell

991
01:26:48,951 --> 01:26:50,282
Open the Gate

992
01:26:50,319 --> 01:26:51,946
Ge Li is back

993
01:27:07,970 --> 01:27:11,235
By order of the Royal Court

994
01:27:11,273 --> 01:27:15,039
Ge Li is defending Liang under false pretenses

995
01:27:15,077 --> 01:27:19,013
and initiates rebellion by
imposing personal adoration

996
01:27:19,047 --> 01:27:21,481
Be arrested, otherwise

997
01:27:21,516 --> 01:27:22,778
you will be killed

998
01:27:28,690 --> 01:27:30,055
General...

999
01:27:42,904 --> 01:27:44,201
Ge Li!

1000
01:27:50,612 --> 01:27:52,807
I'd always suspected your motives

1001
01:27:56,985 --> 01:27:59,852
How dare you seize my land

1002
01:28:00,555 --> 01:28:02,614
I'm going to kill you today

1003
01:28:08,530 --> 01:28:09,690
Take me hostage

1004
01:28:11,900 --> 01:28:13,367
My Prince...

1005
01:28:13,402 --> 01:28:14,699
Thank you

1006
01:28:14,736 --> 01:28:16,636
Draw back

1007
01:28:19,307 --> 01:28:20,399
Move back

1008
01:28:21,910 --> 01:28:22,968
Open the Gate

1009
01:28:23,011 --> 01:28:24,376
Open the Gate

1010
01:28:33,255 --> 01:28:36,053
Ge Li, let go my Prince

1011
01:28:36,091 --> 01:28:37,649
the King will pardon you

1012
01:28:43,799 --> 01:28:46,029
Prepare Ge Li's arrows

1013
01:28:46,068 --> 01:28:47,194
Yes sir

1014
01:28:58,280 --> 01:28:59,372
Thank you

1015
01:28:59,414 --> 01:29:02,247
Mr. Ge Li

1016
01:29:03,118 --> 01:29:04,813
Sir...

1017
01:29:06,488 --> 01:29:08,285
may I follow by your side?

1018
01:29:10,826 --> 01:29:12,225
You should go back

1019
01:29:12,260 --> 01:29:15,058
Staying in Liang is much more important

1020
01:29:15,097 --> 01:29:16,587
Don't you wish to see more people

1021
01:29:16,631 --> 01:29:19,623
passing on Mozi's thought of peace?

1022
01:29:23,405 --> 01:29:24,770
Remember

1023
01:29:24,806 --> 01:29:26,364
those who know how to defend a city

1024
01:29:26,408 --> 01:29:28,239
cannot bring peace to the world

1025
01:29:28,276 --> 01:29:33,873
Peace lies on the kings of all nations

1026
01:29:33,915 --> 01:29:35,041
Understand?

1027
01:29:35,083 --> 01:29:38,519
Ge Li, release the Prince

1028
01:29:39,955 --> 01:29:41,855
Ge Li had released me

1029
01:29:41,890 --> 01:29:43,152
I'm coming back

1030
01:29:43,191 --> 01:29:44,488
Stop

1031
01:29:44,526 --> 01:29:45,652
Sir

1032
01:29:53,268 --> 01:29:54,360
Thank you

1033
01:29:55,203 --> 01:29:56,033
Let's go

1034
01:29:56,071 --> 01:29:57,936
We're not going back

1035
01:29:57,973 --> 01:29:59,372
Where're you guys going?

1036
01:29:59,407 --> 01:30:00,237
Let's go home

1037
01:30:00,275 --> 01:30:01,537
We've got no home

1038
01:30:02,477 --> 01:30:05,275
The Prince is coming back

1039
01:30:05,313 --> 01:30:06,473
Get ready

1040
01:30:06,515 --> 01:30:07,982
Yes

1041
01:30:08,016 --> 01:30:09,506
Aren't they...

1042
01:30:09,551 --> 01:30:12,577
retreated already? Why...

1043
01:30:14,422 --> 01:30:16,390
What sound is that?

1044
01:30:16,424 --> 01:30:19,291
Shoot as far as you can

1045
01:30:19,327 --> 01:30:20,589
Run

1046
01:30:20,629 --> 01:30:21,687
Quick

1047
01:30:24,666 --> 01:30:25,928
Fire

1048
01:30:32,507 --> 01:30:33,974
Run

1049
01:30:38,346 --> 01:30:40,746
Mr. Ge Li

1050
01:30:40,782 --> 01:30:43,307
Don't come back, go

1051
01:30:44,286 --> 01:30:45,776
Go

1052
01:31:03,038 --> 01:31:04,699
Search for the bodies

1053
01:31:04,739 --> 01:31:06,172
Come with me

1054
01:31:15,917 --> 01:31:20,411
My Lordship Liang Shi has fallen

1055
01:31:21,122 --> 01:31:23,215
Your servant has killed
the Prince by accident

1056
01:31:23,258 --> 01:31:25,351
I'll never be forgiven

1057
01:31:27,362 --> 01:31:31,196
However, Liang is still
under the threat of riot

1058
01:31:31,233 --> 01:31:33,394
I plead with you my Lord

1059
01:31:33,435 --> 01:31:36,563
to let me accomplish
my mission in a hundred days

1060
01:31:36,605 --> 01:31:38,800
I swear I can eliminate all Ge Li's league

1061
01:31:41,509 --> 01:31:43,033
I will take my punishment after that

1062
01:31:47,682 --> 01:31:49,650
Please, My Lord

1063
01:31:51,419 --> 01:31:54,718
Liang Shi...

1064
01:31:54,756 --> 01:31:57,452
is my only son

1065
01:31:59,794 --> 01:32:02,820
he was the future of Liang

1066
01:32:05,433 --> 01:32:08,095
You ruined the future of Liang

1067
01:32:08,136 --> 01:32:10,297
Pardoning you?

1068
01:32:13,441 --> 01:32:16,467
That's ridiculous

1069
01:32:24,386 --> 01:32:26,547
But taking into account of your loyalty

1070
01:32:27,856 --> 01:32:32,088
and all you've done in defending Liang

1071
01:32:35,664 --> 01:32:37,655
moreover...

1072
01:32:39,367 --> 01:32:42,097
protection of Liang

1073
01:32:43,071 --> 01:32:46,302
cannot lie on outsiders

1074
01:32:51,680 --> 01:32:55,081
I'm in a hard position

1075
01:32:57,919 --> 01:33:01,878
I'll accept your plea. Hundred days later

1076
01:33:03,758 --> 01:33:05,282
your accusation will be denounced

1077
01:33:07,629 --> 01:33:09,358
Thank you, My Lord

1078
01:33:26,414 --> 01:33:29,850
Why are you taking me?
What have I done?

1079
01:33:46,201 --> 01:33:48,669
General, what's happening here?

1080
01:33:48,703 --> 01:33:50,603
The King's decree

1081
01:33:50,638 --> 01:33:51,866
capture all the rebels

1082
01:33:58,480 --> 01:33:59,970
Rinse again with water

1083
01:34:03,218 --> 01:34:06,085
What have you asked me for, Sir?

1084
01:34:09,391 --> 01:34:11,120
The King ordered you to kill Ge Li

1085
01:34:11,159 --> 01:34:13,252
Why didn't you shoot him last night?

1086
01:34:16,531 --> 01:34:18,089
Ge Li has done nothing wrong

1087
01:34:19,367 --> 01:34:21,358
He saved all the Liang people

1088
01:34:21,403 --> 01:34:22,870
You disobeyed the King's command

1089
01:34:26,474 --> 01:34:27,634
You will be punished

1090
01:34:27,675 --> 01:34:28,607
What do you guys want?

1091
01:34:28,643 --> 01:34:30,270
Let go of me

1092
01:34:30,311 --> 01:34:31,278
Stop

1093
01:34:32,947 --> 01:34:34,414
Stop

1094
01:35:05,847 --> 01:35:08,179
Sometimes, I really don't know...

1095
01:35:09,384 --> 01:35:11,352
what is cause and effect

1096
01:35:17,592 --> 01:35:18,957
There's no cause and effect

1097
01:35:22,630 --> 01:35:26,532
You saved them,
and they turn against you

1098
01:35:28,903 --> 01:35:31,235
Mozi...

1099
01:35:31,272 --> 01:35:34,002
doesn't ask for returns

1100
01:35:37,512 --> 01:35:41,073
Are all Mozis like that?

1101
01:35:41,116 --> 01:35:44,415
How come you came here alone?

1102
01:35:46,521 --> 01:35:48,887
Mozi...

1103
01:35:48,923 --> 01:35:50,823
didn't send anyone to Liang

1104
01:35:54,562 --> 01:35:55,961
You came here on your own will?

1105
01:35:57,332 --> 01:36:00,130
How many cities can you protect?

1106
01:36:00,802 --> 01:36:04,033
There are never ending wars and battles

1107
01:36:04,072 --> 01:36:07,940
peace will only come

1108
01:36:07,976 --> 01:36:10,604
when the seven nations are united

1109
01:36:10,645 --> 01:36:13,341
I believe universal love

1110
01:36:13,381 --> 01:36:15,747
is the only path towards peace

1111
01:36:19,320 --> 01:36:24,656
Mozi's "universal love" is loving everyone

1112
01:36:24,692 --> 01:36:29,857
that means you don't know
whom you should love

1113
01:36:40,508 --> 01:36:42,442
Where are you going?

1114
01:36:42,477 --> 01:36:43,671
To Liang

1115
01:36:43,711 --> 01:36:46,612
and let someone I love
know that I am safe

1116
01:36:50,952 --> 01:36:55,013
It's all underground stream here

1117
01:36:55,056 --> 01:36:56,250
and you're injured

1118
01:36:56,291 --> 01:36:59,192
It's too dangerous, I'll go for you

1119
01:37:12,840 --> 01:37:14,671
Your Majesty

1120
01:37:14,709 --> 01:37:17,405
these people were in league with Ge Li

1121
01:37:17,445 --> 01:37:18,673
They are traitors

1122
01:37:18,713 --> 01:37:20,874
My Lord...

1123
01:37:20,915 --> 01:37:26,080
I have nothing to do with Ge Li

1124
01:37:26,120 --> 01:37:30,648
I know nothing about his rebellion...

1125
01:37:32,527 --> 01:37:33,858
Immoral, selfish

1126
01:37:35,463 --> 01:37:37,522
When everyone praise Ge Li

1127
01:37:37,565 --> 01:37:40,329
respect him and listen to him

1128
01:37:40,368 --> 01:37:41,300
Will you say such things?

1129
01:37:41,336 --> 01:37:46,137
I'm just a farmer,
I just want to live my life

1130
01:37:46,174 --> 01:37:49,974
I don't care who's a hero

1131
01:37:50,011 --> 01:37:52,605
I just miss my family, my child

1132
01:37:52,647 --> 01:37:56,708
my home... My Lord...

1133
01:37:57,852 --> 01:37:59,979
Your city is in great danger

1134
01:38:00,722 --> 01:38:04,351
and you are just self-seeking

1135
01:38:04,959 --> 01:38:08,087
Don't you know
how many unfortunate lives

1136
01:38:08,129 --> 01:38:10,893
we had lost to save our city?

1137
01:38:10,932 --> 01:38:12,866
Without Ge Li

1138
01:38:12,900 --> 01:38:14,925
we never would have been saved

1139
01:38:14,969 --> 01:38:16,459
Guard

1140
01:38:17,905 --> 01:38:19,167
Sir

1141
01:38:19,207 --> 01:38:19,901
Slap her

1142
01:38:19,941 --> 01:38:20,873
Yes

1143
01:38:28,783 --> 01:38:33,720
You are the descendants
of my loyal servant

1144
01:38:33,755 --> 01:38:38,590
and you grew up with my beloved son

1145
01:38:38,626 --> 01:38:42,960
I'll have mercy on you,
I'm granting you death

1146
01:38:42,997 --> 01:38:45,898
you'll have a Royal funeral

1147
01:38:45,933 --> 01:38:49,630
you'll be honored as Calvary Princess

1148
01:38:49,671 --> 01:38:54,165
and buried with my beloved son...

1149
01:38:54,208 --> 01:38:55,766
It's all rubbish

1150
01:38:57,312 --> 01:38:59,439
You just want me

1151
01:38:59,480 --> 01:39:02,938
to be a burial item in your son's tomb

1152
01:39:02,984 --> 01:39:05,350
You want all of us

1153
01:39:05,386 --> 01:39:08,287
to die under you verdict

1154
01:39:10,391 --> 01:39:12,359
so as to prove and

1155
01:39:12,393 --> 01:39:14,452
show your power

1156
01:39:14,495 --> 01:39:16,156
But if it wasn't Ge Li

1157
